---
import site from '@/lib/site';
---

<section class="section af-s3">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="af-s3__header">
      <h2 class="af-s3__heading">
        Why Our Acne Facial Works When Other Treatments Haven't
      </h2>
      <p class="af-s3__subtitle">
        Medical-grade ingredients that target acne at the source without damaging your skin barrier.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="af-s3__features">

      <div class="af-s3__feature">
        <h3 class="af-s3__feature-title">Targets Root Causes, Not Just Symptoms</h3>
        <p class="af-s3__feature-body">
          Our Acne Facial uses medical-grade actives like Salicylic Acid and Tea Tree to penetrate deep into pores, dissolving the buildup of sebum, dead skin cells, and bacteria that cause breakouts at the source.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="af-s3__feature">
        <h3 class="af-s3__feature-title">Balances Oil Without Stripping Your Skin</h3>
        <p class="af-s3__feature-body">
          Say goodbye to that tight, uncomfortable feeling after treatment. Our formula regulates sebum production while maintaining your skin's essential moisture barrier, preventing the rebound oiliness that makes acne worse.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="af-s3__feature">
        <h3 class="af-s3__feature-title">Reduces Inflammation and Accelerates Healing</h3>
        <p class="af-s3__feature-body">
          Centella Asiatica and Houttuynia Cordata calm redness and swelling while promoting cellular repair, helping existing breakouts heal faster and reducing the risk of post-acne scarring.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="af-s3__feature">
        <h3 class="af-s3__feature-title">Safe &amp; Gentle for All Skin Types</h3>
        <p class="af-s3__feature-body">
          Unlike harsh chemical peels or abrasive treatments, our Korean medical-grade skincare protocol is effective yet gentle enough for sensitive, reactive, and acne-prone skin of all types and tones.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="af-s3__cta">
      <a
        href={site.calcomUrl}
        class="btn btn--primary btn--lg"
      >
        Schedule Your Acne Facial Today
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .af-s3__header {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 760px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .af-s3__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .af-s3__subtitle {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .af-s3__features {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .af-s3__feature {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
    padding: var(--space-md);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    background: var(--color-surface);
  }

  .af-s3__feature-title {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: var(--weight-bold);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .af-s3__feature-body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .af-s3__cta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .af-s3__features {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .af-s3__cta .btn {
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>
